subproject.description: International UNVs specialists are placed in District Social Welfare Offices (Technical Advisers) and at the Ministry's headquarters (Information Technical specialists) to ensure quality implementation of the OVC programme activities & for building capacity at District Social Welfare level to safeguard continuity and sustainability; and to assist establish a national OVC electronic management information system at the Ministry respectively.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Capacity Development in Social
